awards.description:
PhD scholarship from the Ministry of Education, Brazilian Government, valued at BRL 100,000
for a 4-year research doctorate degree in Exercise and Sport Science at Universidade de Brasília,
Brazil.

Masters scholarship from the Ministry of Education, Brazilian Government, valued at BRL 18,000
for a 1-year research master’s degree in Exercise and Sport Science at Universidade de Brasília,
Brazil.
